data.description: Charming westside ranch. Coming Soon. Interior photos will be listed next week. This ranch home features 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. Main floor living has wood floors throughout with nice size living room and an eat in kitchen. 3 bedrooms on main and one that has access to the back fenced in yard. Going down into the basement area that offers a wide open space with so much opportunity to make another living area or add additional bedrooms. That half bath is located under the stairs and there is plenty of extra storage. Outside you have a large 2 stall garage and a wonderful view of the city.
